graph TB
    Input[User input: chat / PDF upload / MCP request] --> Validation[Input Validation]
    Validation -->|reject| Rejected[Rejected with reason]
    Validation -->|pass| InjectionScan[Prompt Injection Heuristic Scan]
    InjectionScan -->|suspicious| Sandbox[Wrap as untrusted data block]
    InjectionScan -->|clean| Direct[Pass through]
    Sandbox --> LLM[LLM Call]
    Direct --> LLM
    LLM --> Output[Agent output]
    Output --> PIIMask[PII Masking before logging]
    PIIMask --> SafeLog[Safe Logging - secrets + PII scrubbed]
    Output --> HITL[Human-in-the-loop notice attached]
    HITL --> UIOutput[Shown to user]
